---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="SocialProof for Wedding Videographers — Testimonials That Book Couples Fast | SocialProof"
  description="Collect and display real couple testimonials for your wedding videography business. Build trust that converts inquiries into bookings. Free to start."
>
  <main class="for-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">For Wedding Videographers</p>
        <h1>The most emotional day of their lives deserves the most authentic reviews</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Couples comparing videographers read every word of every review. SocialProof puts your best testimonials front and center on your website — not on WeddingWire where competitors are also listed.</p>
        <div class="cta-group">
          <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
          <a href="/docs/quickstart" class="btn btn-secondary">See how it works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pain">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Why wedding videographers lose bookings they should win</h2>
        <div class="pain-grid">
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>😤 Reviews live on platforms that benefit competitors</h3>
            <p>You have 4.9 stars on WeddingWire. But couples browsing that platform see your competitors' ads right next to your listing. Bring your social proof to your own site.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>📸 Couples share feedback in private messages</h3>
            <p>"The video made us cry — you captured everything perfectly." Incredible. But that WhatsApp message isn't converting new clients. A proper testimonial on your portfolio site does.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>🔗 Your samples sell better with context</h3>
            <p>A stunning highlight reel is compelling. A stunning reel paired with a couple's heartfelt testimonial is irresistible.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="solution">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>SocialProof fixes this in 3 steps</h2>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>
            <strong>Send a collect link</strong>
            <p>Share your unique form link via text, email, or QR code. Send the collect link when you deliver the final video — it's the highest-emotion moment in the whole relationship.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Approve with one click</strong>
            <p>Review submissions in your dashboard. Approve the keepers. Hide the rest.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Embed on your site</strong>
            <p>One script tag. Paste it anywhere — your homepage, booking page, bio link. Add testimonials to your portfolio page, pricing page, or anywhere couples are making their decision.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Built for Wedding Videographers</h2>
        <div class="feature-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>⭐ Star ratings + text</h3>
            <p>Collect written testimonials with optional star ratings. Shows visitors exactly what to expect.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📷 Customer photos</h3>
            <p>Let clients add a photo or headshot. Real faces build real trust.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🎨 Matches your brand</h3>
            <p>Customize colors, fonts, and layout so the widget looks native on your site.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📱 Works on any device</h3>
            <p>Your customers fill the form on their phone. The widget looks great on mobile too.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🔒 You own the data</h3>
            <p>Testimonials live in your account, not on a third-party platform. No lock-in.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🆓 Free forever tier</h3>
            <p>1 active widget, unlimited collections. Free forever for 1 active widget. No credit card to start.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pricing-cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Start collecting testimonials today</h2>
        <p>Free forever for 1 active widget. Pro is $9/mo for unlimited everything.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get started free</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
